- Using **comparative judgment paradigms** (e.g., forced-choice comparisons) instead of absolute ratings to better assess explanatory distinction.
- Applying **adaptive comparative judgment (ACJ)** from psychometrics to increase annotation efficiency and reliability by selecting optimal explanation pairs dynamically.
