rategies between domains. This enables zero-shot generalization to new tasks by prompting generators with distilled templates. By aligning explanation generation with human cognitive priors—not just surface-level correctness—CogniReward moves beyond traditional metrics like BLEU or ROUGE-L, targeting deeper interpretability and user trust. The framework has broad implications for building self-improving AI systems in high-stakes applications such as medical diagnosis assistants or legal reasoning tools, where the quality of justification is as important as the answer itself.",
